Sentencas: Cathode materials consisting of Sr1-x TbxCoO3-delta (x = 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) were prepared from a stoichiometric mixture of SrCO3, Co3O4, and Tb4O7 for intermediate- temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Terbium-Doped SrCoO3 as a New Cathode Material for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The crystal structure of Sr0.9Tb0.1CoO3-delta was defined in the cubic Pm-3m space group (No. 221), and Sr0.8Tb0.2CoO3-delta and Sr0.7Tb0.3CoO3-delta had a tetragonal I4/mmm structure.
Titulo: Terbium-Doped SrCoO3 as a New Cathode Material for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity values were all higher than 407 S.cm(-1) for T >= 500 degrees C.
Titulo: Terbium-Doped SrCoO3 as a New Cathode Material for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The area specific resistances (ASRs) and its activation energy (E-a) increased with increasing x.
Titulo: Terbium-Doped SrCoO3 as a New Cathode Material for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The oxygen vacancies and the thermal expansion coefficients (TECs) decreased with increasing x. The TECs were influenced by the concentration of oxygen vacancies and the transition of the Co3+ ions from a low-spin to a high-spin state.
Titulo: Terbium-Doped SrCoO3 as a New Cathode Material for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The cathodes exhibited porosity microstructure and good adhesion to solid electrolyte.
Titulo: Terbium-Doped SrCoO3 as a New Cathode Material for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: Sr0.9Tb0.1CoO3-delta had the best cathode characteristics and the most stable performance.
Titulo: Terbium-Doped SrCoO3 as a New Cathode Material for IT-SOFC
